# Elements

Story elements: the who, what, and where of The Kepler Testimonies.

## Contents

| Section | Purpose |
|---------|---------|
| [[characters/_index\|Characters]] | The voices behind the testimonies |
| [[places/_index\|Places]] | Locations and settings |
