| [[objects/_index\|Objects]] | Significant items |

## Usage

Element files describe **what things are**, not what happens to them. Story events go in [[../outline/_index|Outline]]; element files provide the building blocks.

When drafting reveals new details about an element, update its file to maintain consistency across the project.

